# The Coffee Links — Ultra-Fast Ordering Intelligence

> **Objective:** A user can place a correct order in 1–2 taps, without browsing, searching, or rethinking choices.

---

## 1️⃣ ORDER TYPES EXPANSION

### Current State
The app supports three order types via [DeliveryOption](file:///Users/nguyenducnhat/appcafe/thecoffeelinks-client-ios/thecoffeelinks-client-ios/Models/Order.swift#L10-L14):
- `dineIn` — Table-linked QR ordering
- `takeAway` — Counter pickup
- `delivery` — **Exists in model but NOT implemented in UI**

### Delivery Implementation Requirements

#### Address Handling
| Component | Requirement |
|-----------|-------------|
| Saved addresses | HomeView should surface "Deliver to: [Address]" with 1-tap change |
| Address picker | Pull from [SavedAddressesView](file:///Users/nguyenducnhat/appcafe/thecoffeelinks-client-ios/thecoffeelinks-client-ios/Views/SavedAddressesView.swift) |
| Address validation | Server-side geocoding + delivery zone check |
| Default address | Auto-select last-used; learn from frequency |

#### ETA Clarity
```
Pattern: "Ready in X min" → "Arrives by HH:MM"
```
- Show real-time rider tracking after dispatch
- Pessimistic ETA (add 10min buffer) to prevent disappointment

#### Menu Availability Differences
> [!WARNING]
> Not all items survive delivery. Ice drinks dilute, pastries compress.

**Solution:**
- `isDeliverable: Bool` flag per product
- Gray out non-deliverable items with tooltip: "Best enjoyed in-store"
- Server filters menu by delivery zone (some items unavailable in far zones)

#### Packaging & Temperature UX
- Show "Packaged for delivery" badge on compatible items
- Hot drinks: "Sealed at 85°C, stays hot for 30min"
- Cold drinks: "Ice-packed, arrives cold"

### Home/Menu/Checkout Changes for Delivery Mode

| Screen | When Delivery Selected |
|--------|------------------------|
| **Home** | Show "Delivering to [Address]" header; hide in-store-only sections |
| **Menu** | Filter to `isDeliverable == true`; add delivery surcharge to prices |
| **Checkout** | Show address confirmation, ETA estimate, delivery fee breakdown |

### What to Hide
- Table selection (dine-in only)
- "Nearest store" picker (auto-select delivery hub)
- In-store-only promotions

