## 4️⃣ POPULAR RIGHT NOW & SOCIAL PROOF

### Trending Surfaces

| Surface | Source | Refresh Rate |
|---------|--------|--------------|
| Location-based | Orders at this store, last 2 hours | 15 minutes |
| Time-window | Orders at similar time yesterday | 1 hour |
| User-profile similar | Users with similar order history | Daily |

### Anti-Manipulation Design

> [!CAUTION]
> Popularity can be gamed. Ensure authenticity.

#### Prevent Herd Bias
- Show "Popular" badge only if item has >5 orders in window
- Never show more than 3 "Popular" items simultaneously
- Rotate trending items to prevent winner-take-all

#### Avoid Menu Noise
- Popular badge is **subtle** (small icon, not banner)
- Don't stack badges (no "Popular + New + Seasonal")
- Popularity is a **tiebreaker**, not primary driver

#### Trust Signals
```
"☕ 47 ordered today at this store" — specific, credible
vs.
"🔥 Popular!" — generic, suspicious
```

### When Popularity Helps vs. Hurts Speed

| Scenario | Popularity Effect |
|----------|-------------------|
| New user, no history | **Helps:** provides starting point |
| Regular with strong preferences | **Hurts:** distracts from usual |
| Seasonal item launch | **Helps:** surfaces discovery |
| Crowded menu | **Hurts:** adds cognitive load |

**Solution:** Hide popularity badges if user has 5+ orders (they know what they want).

