## 5️⃣ ZERO-THINKING ORDERING (CRITICAL)

### AI-Generated Ready-to-Order Carts

#### Current State
[QuickOrderService](file:///Users/nguyenducnhat/appcafe/thecoffeelinks-client-ios/thecoffeelinks-client-ios/Services/QuickOrderService.swift) uses frequency × recency scoring but lacks:
- Time-of-day awareness
- Weather integration
- Day-of-week patterns
- Multi-item cart prediction

#### Enhanced Prediction Model

```
Score = (frequency × recencyWeight) + timeBonusð + weatherBonus + dayOfWeekBonus

Where:
- timeBonus = +2.0 if ordered at similar hour (±1hr window)
- weatherBonus = +1.5 if weather matches (hot→cold drink, cold→hot)
- dayOfWeekBonus = +1.0 if same weekday pattern
```

#### Cart Composition Logic
| User Pattern | Predicted Cart |
|--------------|----------------|
| Always orders 1 item | Single item cart |
| Usually orders coffee + pastry | Combo cart |
| Morning = coffee, afternoon = tea | Time-switched single |

### Time-Based Prediction

[AppState.timeMode](file:///Users/nguyenducnhat/appcafe/thecoffeelinks-client-ios/thecoffeelinks-client-ios/AppState.swift#L14-L18) already defines:
- Morning (6-11am)
- Day (11am-5pm)
- Evening (5pm+)

**Enhancement:** Track per-slot ordering.

```swift
struct TimeSlotOrder {
    let slot: TimeSlot // morning/day/evening
    let dayOfWeek: Int // 1-7
    let items: [QuickOrderItem]
    let frequency: Int
}
```

### Context-Based Prediction Signals

| Signal | Source | Prediction Power |
|--------|--------|------------------|
| Time of day | System clock | High |
| Day of week | System calendar | Medium |
| Weather | WeatherKit API | Medium |
| Location | CoreLocation | High (if at store) |
| Meeting calendar | EventKit | Low (privacy concern) |
| Streak continuation | QuickOrderService | Medium |

### Confirm Flow Options

#### Option A: One-Tap Danger Zone
```
[☕ Your morning order]
[Iced Latte + Croissant - 89k]
[ORDER NOW] ← single tap places order
```
**Risk:** Accidental orders, wrong store, no customization chance.

#### Option B: Two-Step Confirm (Recommended)
```
[☕ Your morning order]
[Iced Latte + Croissant - 89k]
[ADD TO CART] ← tap 1
    ↓
[Cart preview] → [CHECKOUT] ← tap 2
```
**Benefit:** User sees cart before commit; can modify.

#### Option C: Slide-to-Order
```
[☕ Your morning order]
[>>> Slide to order >>>]
```
**Benefit:** Intentional gesture prevents accidents.

### Undo / Cancel Safety

| Stage | Undo Mechanism |
|-------|----------------|
| Cart added | Standard cart edit |
| Order placed (0-30s) | "Undo" toast appears |
| Order placed (30s-2min) | "Cancel order" in Orders tab |
| Order accepted by store | Call store (no in-app cancel) |

### Trust & Control Balance

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The moment users feel the AI made a mistake they didn't catch, trust evaporates.

#### Safe Defaults
- AI cart is **pre-filled, not auto-ordered**
- User must tap at least once to confirm
- Cart shows "AI suggested" badge

#### Opt-In Features
- "Auto-order my usual at 8:30am" — explicit toggle
- "Order when I arrive at store" — geofence trigger
- "Remind me to order at usual time" — notification

#### Trust Erosion Prevention
| Trigger | Response |
|---------|----------|
| User dismisses AI cart 3x | Stop showing for 7 days |
| User always modifies AI cart | Learn from modifications |
| AI predicts wrong item | Show "We'll do better" message |

