## 6️⃣ ON-DEVICE AI (APPLE INTELLIGENCE)

### Feasibility Assessment

| Capability | On-Device | Server-Side |
|------------|-----------|-------------|
| Order history analysis | ✅ Yes | Optional backup |
| Time pattern detection | ✅ Yes | Not needed |
| Weather-based prediction | ❌ No (needs API) | ✅ Yes |
| Location-based trending | ❌ No | ✅ Yes (aggregated) |
| Price calculation | ❌ No | ✅ Yes (source of truth) |

### What MUST Be Local
1. **Order history storage** — already in UserDefaults via QuickOrderService
2. **Personal pattern detection** — frequency × recency scoring
3. **Favorites/notes** — never leave device
4. **Customization defaults** — [UserPreferencesManager](file:///Users/nguyenducnhat/appcafe/thecoffeelinks-client-ios/thecoffeelinks-client-ios/Services/UserPreferencesManager.swift)

### Server-Side Requirements
1. **Trending calculation** — requires aggregate data
2. **Menu availability** — real-time inventory
3. **Price calculation** — business logic changes
4. **ETA estimation** — store load, rider availability

### Privacy Messaging

```
"Your ordering habits stay on your phone.
We never see what you ordered — only when you checkout."
```

**UI Pattern:** Show padlock icon next to AI suggestions.

```
🔒 Suggested based on your history (never shared)
```

### Hybrid Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              On-Device (Swift)          │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────┐    │
│  │  Order History (UserDefaults)   │    │
│  │  Pattern Detection (local ML)   │    │
│  │  Favorites + Notes (local)      │    │
│  │  Prediction Scoring (local)     │    │
│  └────────────────┬────────────────┘    │
│                   │ prediction request  │
└───────────────────┼─────────────────────┘
                    ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              Server (Vercel)            │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────┐    │
│  │  Menu + Pricing (Supabase)      │    │
│  │  Inventory Check                │    │
│  │  Trending (aggregated)          │    │
│  │  Weather API integration        │    │
│  └─────────────────────────────────┘    │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

