## 7️⃣ SPEED AUDIT — WHERE TIME IS WASTED

### Current Flow Analysis

#### Flow: Regular User Ordering Their Usual

| Step | Taps | Hesitation Points | Time (est) |
|------|------|-------------------|------------|
| Open app | 1 | App load time | 0.5s |
| See QuickOrderWidget | 0 | Scan for correct item | 1-2s |
| Tap to add to cart | 1 | None | 0.3s |
| See "Noted" feedback | 0 | Is it in cart? | 0.5s |
| Open cart floater | 1 | Find the button | 0.5s |
| Review cart | 0 | Verify correctness | 1-2s |
| Tap checkout | 1 | Navigate to CheckoutView | 0.3s |
| Select payment | 1 | Which method? | 1-2s |
| Tap place order | 1 | Final hesitation | 0.5s |
| **TOTAL** | **7 taps** | | **5-8s** |

### Micro-Frictions Identified

#### 🔴 UNFORGIVABLE (Must Fix)

| Friction | Location | Impact | Fix |
|----------|----------|--------|-----|
| Loading spinner on Home | HomeView | Blocks first interaction | Pre-fetch on app launch |
| No visual cart count on Home | HomeView | User unsure if item added | Add badge to cart floater |
| Payment selection every time | CheckoutView | Repeated decision | Remember last used |
| Must select store for pickup | CheckoutView | Extra step | Auto-select nearest |
| No 1-tap reorder from Orders | OrdersView | Historical orders require recreation | Add "Order Again" button |

#### 🟡 ACCEPTABLE (But Could Improve)

| Friction | Location | Impact | Optimization |
|----------|----------|--------|--------------|
| Customization sheet for changes | OrderCustomizationView | Extra modal | Inline quick-edit |
| Scroll to see all cart items | CartFloater | Hidden items | Collapse if >3 items |
| Highlights carousel autoplay | HomeView | Distraction | Pause if user scrolling |

#### 🟢 ACCEPTABLE (Part of UX)

| Friction | Location | Justification |
|----------|----------|---------------|
| Order confirmation tap | CheckoutView | Prevents accidents |
| View order after placed | OrdersView | User wants confirmation |
| Login required | ContentView | Security necessity |

### Speed Optimization Opportunities

#### Immediate Wins
1. **Pre-fill payment method** — Use [lastPaymentMethod](file:///Users/nguyenducnhat/appcafe/thecoffeelinks-client-ios/thecoffeelinks-client-ios/Services/UserPreferencesManager.swift#L32-L34)
2. **Auto-select nearest store** — Use location from StoresViewModel
3. **Cart count badge** — Show on CartFloater persistently
4. **Haptic on add** — Already exists, ensure prominence

#### Medium-Term Wins
1. **1-tap reorder from Orders** — Add button per historical order
2. **Skip checkout for Quick Order** — Long-press already exists, promote it
3. **Predictive prefetch** — Load likely products before user taps

#### Long-Term Wins
1. **Voice ordering** — "Order my usual"
2. **Widget ordering** — iOS Home Screen widget
3. **Watch ordering** — Single-tap from Apple Watch

