## TRADE-OFFS & RISKS

| Feature | Risk | Mitigation |
|---------|------|------------|
| AI prediction | Wrong item ordered | Always show preview; easy undo |
| Geofence ordering | Battery drain | Use significant location changes only |
| Auto-select store | Wrong store selected | Show store name prominently; easy change |
| Payment memory | Card expired/wrong | Validate before charging |
| Calendar integration | Privacy concern | Opt-in only; clear permissions dialog |
| Voice ordering | Misinterpretation | Confirm before checkout |

